@TheWrathofShane  

MTG already has demons, angels, priests, spirits, ghouls, demi-gods, avatars...  

So suddenly with the addition of "devil" it becomes too much? What about cards like [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God)? Why do you even have to explain to them anyway? Unless you're playing MTG at church, I honestly don't see how its any of their business. **Its just a game.** To be played by YOU in your OWN PERSONAL TIME. How absurd of them to be hung up about such minor inconsequential things. They'd probably think Harry Potter and rock songs are the work of the devil too...pfft

